This is manual_refresh README file.

This demo shows two widgets connected to the same source, refreshed in __manual mode__


DEPENDENCIES:

none

Tango devices used
------------------
TANGO HOST:

export TANGO_HOST=hokuto:20000

SOURCES:
test/device/1/double_scalar
sys/tg_test/1/double_scalar



Building
--------

qmake 
make
                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                
Main customer                                                                                                                   
